gw.api.assignment

Class AutoAssignAssignee

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.assignment.AutoAssignAssignee
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Assignee

    public class AutoAssignAssignee
extends java.lang.Object
implements Assignee
    Assignee used to auto assign an assignable bean, that is to assign it using the assignment rules appropriate for the type of bean (activity assignment rules for activities and so on). Implements the standard Assignee interface.

    • Field Summary

      static AutoAssignAssignee INSTANCE
      Singleton instance of the AutoAssignAssignee. Because this assignee has no internal state the single instance can be shared, even between multiple threads.
